episodes.title: Cults, Prophecies, and Power: South Korea’s Political Chaos, Shamans, Scandals, and a Shocking Coup!
episodes.description:
Dive into the jaw-dropping story of South Korea’s biggest political scandal yet! The bizarre downfall of President Yoon Suk Yeol, from his midnight martial law blunder to his historic arrest. Shadowy shamans, fortune-tellers, and cult leaders pulling the strings behind the scenes. Why does Korea keep falling for mystical meddling?
